                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        f. 32ra-b: ተፈጽመ፡ ድርሳነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በዘመነ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ…f. 32ra-b: The homily of Our Saviour was completed in the peace of God in the time of our King Ḫayla Śǝllāse…
                        The colophon mentions King Ḫayla Śǝllāse I (r. 1930-74).
                     </colophon>
